Start a new rotation with the supplied PSK

Usage:
  grainfs cluster rotate-key begin [flags]

Flags:
      --generate         auto-generate a new 32-byte PSK
  -h, --help             help for begin
      --new-key string   new cluster PSK (64 hex chars / 32 bytes); mutually exclusive with --generate

Global Flags:
      --endpoint string    rotate-key socket path (NOT admin.sock; default <data-dir>/rotate.sock); server logs the path on startup as "rotate endpoint"
      --format string      Output format: text or json (status/peers/events; ignored elsewhere) (default "text")
      --log-level string   log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")
